  <CE_Apparel_MeleeShield.label>melee shield</Apparel_MeleeShield.label>
  <CE_Apparel_MeleeShield.description>Simple shield that can block simple projectiles and hits with melee weapons.</Apparel_MeleeShield.description>

  <CE_Apparel_BallisticShield.label>ballistic shield</Apparel_BallisticShield.label>
  <CE_Apparel_BallisticShield.description>A heavy shield designed to protect against gunfire. It can cover most of the wearer's body but restricts use of two-handed weapons. Its heavy weight and bulk make it unwieldy in combat.</Apparel_BallisticShield.description>


